  }, "TeamPCPs"), ", and a whole lot less vibe in vibe-coding. I hope I am totally wrong though."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "I asked claude to write what it feels about my words. Everything below is claude, funny."), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
